item.title: I need help with moparscape
item.dc:creator: @irockursox13 irockursox13
item.description:
@irockursox13 wrote:

There is no problem with that command, it takes a while to set up codes, but if your experiencing difficulties trying to get in servers that cause errors it usually means that they never exist or offline, you will need to download kamachi and do tutorial…also find some one who has a group set for ip, like kahoku, it sets up a command prompt if you click which ip server you get in, once the prompt command is up put that ip on your server ip box, you should be in. If you lag you need to sign on a couple of times lol…
